message.body: Not too bad. Sorry I was away from my phone while I was working. Do you plans for the weekend?
Yeah, my parents are in town, so I'm going to show them around the city. I'm based in San Francisco. Where do you stay?
I live in SF too but im working in Mtn View this summer. What are you going to show your parents? Have they been to SF before?
(1/2)Nope, it's their first time. Will show them around the Embarcadero, Pier 39, Ghirardelli and such. Have you lived here all your life? How are you
What about you? Did you go to Penn?
